quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  7,58,"Asaase pa no nso, εso nnuaba no fifiri wͻ ne Wura Nyankopͻn akwamma mu. Na (asaase a) εnyε no ɛmfifiri hwee, gyesε kakraa bi. Saa ara na Yεkyerεkyerε nsεm no mu de ma amanfoͻ a wͻyi (Nyame) ayε."
  7,59,"Ampa sε, Yεsomaa Noah kͻͻ ne nkorͻfoͻ hͻ. Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, monsom Nyankopͻn, na monni awurade foforͻ biara wͻ N’akyi. Nokorε sε mesuro Da kεseε no asotwee no ma mo “."
  7,60,"Nhemfo a εwͻ nenkorͻfoͻ no mu no kaa sε: “Yɛhu wo sε wowͻ ͻyera pefee paa mu “."
  7,61,"Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, εnyε yera na mayera, na mmom meyε Ɔsomafoͻ firi Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no hͻ."
  7,62,"Me Wura Nyankopͻn Asεm no ho dawuro na merebɔ akyerε mo, na merema mo afutupa, na menim adeε a monnim wͻ Nyankopͻn hͻ."
  7,63,"Anaasε εyε mo nwanwa sε Afutusεm firi mo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ nam momu nipa bi so aba mo hͻ sεdeε ͻde bεbͻ mo kͻkͻ na mobεyε ahwεyie ama yɛahu mo mmͻbͻ?"
  7,64,"Nanso wͻbuu no nkontomponi, enti Yεgyee no, ne wͻn a wͻka ne ho no wͻ εhyεn no mu no nkwa, na Yεmaa nsuo faa wͻn a wͻfaa Yεn Nsεm no atorͻsεm no. Nokorε sε, na wͻyε nnipa a wͻn ani afira."
  7,65,"Aadfoͻ nso wͻn nua Huud kͻͻ wͻn hͻ. Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, monsom Nyankopͻn, (efirisε) monni awurade foforͻ biara wͻ N’akyi. Enti monnnsuro Nyankopͻn na monnyε ahwεyie?”"
  7,66,"Nhemfo {anaa mpanimfoͻ} boniayεfoͻ a εwͻ nenkorͻfoͻ no mu no kaa sε: “Nokorε, yɛhu wo sε wo wͻ agyimisεm mu na yεdwen sε woka nkontompofoͻ no ho."
  7,67,"Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, εnyε gyimii na magyimi, na mmom meyε Ɔsomafoͻ firi Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no hͻ “."
